These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, funk, gospel, hip-hop
There 4 different types of food: raspberry, spinach, kiwi, pomegranate
1. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the fan of gospel##1
2. the fan of electronic is on the left of the person eating spinach##1
3. the fan of hip-hop is in an odd position##4
4. the person eating kiwi is on the left or right of the person eating pomegranate##3
5. the fan of electronic is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | funk | hip-hop | gospel |
| Food        | raspberry | spinach   | pomegranate | kiwi    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: purple, ivory, white, light-blue
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, august, january, april
1. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1
2. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
3. the person who's birthday is in january is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's birthday is in july is the person who likes purple##1
5. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
6. the person who's birthday is in july is the person who likes purple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Color   | white | purple  | ivory  | light-blue |
| Birthday   | april    | july | january | august    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, badminton, soccer, skiing
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, orchid, lily, balloon-flower
1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left or right of the person who growsballoon-flower##3
2. the person who's sport is soccer is in an even position##4
3. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left or right of the person who's sport is badminton##3
4. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person who growslily##1
5. the person who growszinnia is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Sport          | skiing | soccer | badminton    | surfing      |
| Flower   | lily        | balloon-flower     | zinnia | orchid |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
City: edinburgh, liverpool, paris, new-york
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, juice, tea, hot-chocolate
1. the person traveling to liverpool is between the person drinking 7up and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
2. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
3. the person drinking tea is in an odd position##4
4. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
5. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| City         | new-york | edinburgh | liverpool | paris |
| Beverage   | tea       | 7up   | juice    | hot-chocolate  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, lacrosse, skiing, climbing
There are 4 different favourite colors: orange, green, yellow, red
1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person who likes red##1
2. the person who likes green is the person who's sport is climbing##1
3. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
4. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is skiing is in an odd position##4
6. the person who likes orange is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Sport   | lacrosse  | weightlifting    | skiing   | climbing       |
| Color   | orange | red | yellow | green |

