.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-6::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, oliveros, bolivar, vegafina
The people have 4 different jobs:  librarian, dressmaker, bartender, designer
1. the dressmaker is in an even position##4
2. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the dressmaker##1
3. the bolivar-smoker is in an odd position##4
4. the librarian is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1
5. the bartender is on the left or right of the librarian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Cigar   | bolivar      | oliveros | vegafina | pall-mall |
| Job   | designer | dressmaker     | librarian  | bartender  |

