.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, salsa, blues, hip-hop
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, iris, rose, bellflower
1. the person who growsbellflower is in an odd position##4
2. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
3. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of blues##1
4. the person who growsbellflower is the fan of rock##1
5. the fan of hip-hop is on the left or right of the person who growstulip##3
6. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person who growstulip##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | rock | hip-hop | blues | salsa    |
| Flower     | bellflower | rose  | tulip     | iris |

