.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-8::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, satire, scientific, western
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, mirinda, water, soy-milk
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person watching satire movies##3
2. the person watching western movies is in an odd position##4
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3
4. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
5. the person watching epic movies is between the person watching western movies and the person watching satire movies##2
6. the person drinking mirinda is in an odd position##4
7. the person drinking mirinda is between the person watching epic movies and the person drinking water##2
8. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the person watching satire movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | epic      | western | scientific |
| Beverage   | sprite  | soy-milk | mirinda    | water            |

