.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-9::.
City: san-francisco, rome, liverpool, prague
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, june, may, december
1. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left or right of the person traveling to san-francisco##3
2. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
3. the person who's birthday is in march is between the person who's birthday is in june and the person traveling to liverpool##2
4. the person who's birthday is in march is in an odd position##4
5. the person traveling to liverpool is the person who's birthday is in may##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| City   | prague | rome   | san-francisco | liverpool |
| Birthday    | december     | june | march     | may  |

