.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
4 different games are played: monopoly, domino, backgammon, billiard
There 4 different types of food: potato, apricot, lemon, peach
1. the person playing monopoly is the person eating peach##1
2. the person eating potato is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
3. the person eating peach is between the person eating potato and the person playing backgammon##2
4. the person playing monopoly is in an odd position##4
5. the person eating peach is on the left or right of the person eating potato##3
6. the person playing domino is on the left or right of the person eating apricot##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Game      | domino       | backgammon   | monopoly | billiard |
| Food   | lemon | apricot | peach        | potato    |

