.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-11::.
City: edinburgh, hannover, paris, colone
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, jet-ski, helicopter, trike
1. the person driving the tram is in an even position##4
2. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
3. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
4. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
5. the person traveling to hannover is on the left or right of the person traveling to paris##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |
| City   | edinburgh   | colone   | hannover      | paris      |
| Transport      | jet-ski | helicopter | trike | tram |

