.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-12::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: ivory, lavender, blood-red, lilac
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, quad-bike, bike, subway
1. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
2. the person driving the bike is in an even position##4
3. the person who likes lavender is in an even position##4
4. the person who likes ivory is on the far right##1
5. the person who likes blood-red is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person driving the bike##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Color          | lilac | lavender  | blood-red  | ivory |
| Transport   | subway  | bike | airplane | quad-bike   |

