.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-13::.
4 different pets are kept: goat, dog, snake, frog
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, tennis, rowing, skiing
1. the person who's sport is tennis is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
3. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left or right of the owner of the goat##3
4. the owner of the dog is in an odd position##4
5. the person who's sport is tennis is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the owner of the snake##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |     4     |
| Pet   | dog | goat | snake | frog  |
| Sport     | tennis   | soccer  | skiing  | rowing |

