.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-14::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, sprite, soy-milk, tea
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, old-henry, alhambra, cain
1. the alhambra-smoker is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking cola is in an odd position##4
3. the person drinking tea is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1
4. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the cain-smoker##1
5. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
6. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left or right of the cain-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |      4       |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | tea | cola | sprite |
| Cigar           | cain     | tiparillo     | alhambra   | old-henry         |

