The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daisy, iris, azalea, amaryllis
The people have 4 different jobs:  videographer, bartender, engineer, freelancer
1. the person who growsdaisy is between the videographer and the person who growsiris##2
2. the person who growsazalea is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who growsiris is on the left of the freelancer##1
4. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
5. the freelancer is in an odd position##4
6. the engineer is on the left of the bartender##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |       3       |      4       |
| Flower   | amaryllis | iris         | daisy   | azalea |
| Job   | engineer    | bartender | freelancer | videographer   |

