.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-16::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, azalea, bellflower, sunflower
4 different pets are kept: cat, pony, goldfish, rat
1. the owner of the rat is the person who growsbellflower##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is the person who growsamaryllis##1
3. the owner of the pony is the person who growssunflower##1
4. the person who growsbellflower is on the left or right of the person who growssunflower##3
5. the person who growsamaryllis is in an even position##4
6. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Flower   | azalea | amaryllis | bellflower    | sunflower |
| Pet   | cat   | goldfish  | rat | pony     |

