.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-17::.
House: tower, gothic-revival, ranch-style, cape-cod
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, rock, folk, punk
1. the ranch-style house is on the left of the tower house##1
2. the ranch-style house is in an even position##4
3. the fan of rock is the ranch-style house##1
4. the fan of folk is on the left or right of the fan of rock##3
5. the fan of rock is between the fan of punk and the fan of folk##2
6. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the fan of punk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| House         | cape-cod   | ranch-style | tower | gothic-revival    |
| Music-Genre   | folk | rock  | punk     | trance |

