.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, vegafina, alhambra, montecristo
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: indie, blues, salsa, classical
1. the fan of blues is on the far left##1
2. the alhambra-smoker is on the left or right of the dannemann-smoker##3
3. the montecristo-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
4. the fan of salsa is on the left of the fan of classical##1
5. the fan of classical is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1
6. the fan of salsa is in an even position##4
7. the fan of indie is the vegafina-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Cigar   | montecristo | dannemann    | alhambra       | vegafina |
| Music-Genre       | blues  | salsa | classical | indie  |

