.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-19::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, video-games, hiking, singing
There 4 different types of food: plum, cranberry, kale, cucumber
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
2. the person eating kale is on the left or right of the person eating plum##3
3. the person eating plum is on the left of the person eating kale##1
4. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
5. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person eating kale##1
6. the person eating plum is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Hobby   | video-games | hiking | fishing  | singing |
| Food     | plum      | kale       | cranberry | cucumber     |

