.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
City: berlin, san-francisco, miami, hannover
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, begonia, marigold, daisy
1. the person traveling to san-francisco is in an even position##4
2. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left or right of the person who growsorchid##3
3. the person who growsbegonia is between the person traveling to berlin and the person who growsorchid##2
4. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
6. the person who growsmarigold is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| City         | berlin | miami   | hannover | san-francisco |
| Flower   | daisy          | begonia | orchid         | marigold  |

 